<FILE Name="&emhttp;/README.md">
<INLINE>
**Prometheus Wireguard Exporter**

Is a slim plugin, that takes the informations gathered from the wireguard API and provides it to a prometheus database. Usage is not limited to prometheus only. Data can be formated and displayed to any database or graphical node.  
ATTENTION: Ports must be set up correctly to run this application. It is recommended to run prometheus directly as a Docker container.  
This Plugin is based on prometheus_wireguard_exporter from MindFlavor: https://github.com/MindFlavor/prometheus_wireguard_exporter
</INLINE>
</FILE>

